<p>This camp is located not far from Stalkers as someone said previously, just right across the river.  The camp has 5 spawns of the larger spiders the first two are around a tree, while the other 3 are behind them on the hillside.  Amongst the three on the hill there was a named giant spider--Terror Matriarch which if killed has a 3 day spawn..no one has really said if these consorts can be snared or not...will find out later.</p>
