<p>This looks fairly 'Gothy' if that makes sense. In the old models and new it looks very cool. In the older it looks like a semi transparent top. On the new it even has two shoulder rings that look like they lead to less transparent material. They look awesome. Very unique, not like same skin other color.... <br /> <br />I wanted one for looks alone, didnt realize the stats were nice also.</p>
